sky\n- Leave contact information, VIB will call then\n", "short_description": "VIB Verse is the Virtual reality app - a product of Vietnam International Bank (VIB). Users need to use VR headset to immerse themselves in VIB city banking with numerous zones dedicated to separate products such as Auto Loan and Credit Card, as well as entertainment areas like beach, bar, park, and fountain. Users can customize their appearance by editing character's face, hair, clothes, and shoes, as well as selecting a nickname. Surely, VIB Verse app will provide a delightful experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.vib.com.vn/i/en/vib-verse/chinh-sach-bao-mat", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VIB Bank", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.vib.com.vn/i/en/vib-verse", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "421923165850360"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "vi"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "7516763178449258"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "354458587384418"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "354458587384418"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1721644725, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "354458587384418"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7603135299812045", "version": "1.0023"}, "id": "1843548639476736", "channel